Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛的煙火大會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.19,0:01:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙真是太過份了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然丟下我一個人跑到海邊去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.86,0:01:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是十年才一次的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.95,0:02:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼還不來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要是看到我這身泳裝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包準會迷死的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.39,0:03:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊 擺脫妳莊重點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想也知道 那傢伙八成正在泡妞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想到海邊去玩水哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 正義女神 讓他們這樣玩好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用工作的時候 時間就是他們自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們喜歡怎麼樣都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這樣子 他們好像有點玩過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神是無所不在的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是聖賢或是愚昧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真實的愛或者心靈的創痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須親身去體會人們的種種心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能真正保護這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔚藍的海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的雲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有小屁股 喔 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小麥色皮膚的夏日女郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在呼喚著我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的小姐們…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸襟寬大?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖是實話 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位小姐們…我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 和我約個會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我約會 跟我約會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位小姐跟我約會好不好嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點兒小事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪擋得住我的熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好燙好燙…燙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請接受我的熱情邀約…我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們留下夏日美好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有完沒完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真低級\N煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題沒問題 已經完全沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是這位小姐 妳是不是對我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫彭芭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了報上我的姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫凱洛特…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特葛拉瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特先生 其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一件事情想要拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要拜託我什麼事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上的煙火大會上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什麼事情?\N我希望你能夠來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午夜 2點 我就在這裡等你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要妳不嫌棄我 我就來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎? 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們約好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就晚上見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定哦\N好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的他真是可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂拉 對吧\N沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海灘球真的事掉在這附近嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…我記得是在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不對? 姊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? …是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼嘛 等一下我要和可愛的彭芭約會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要準備很多事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 凱洛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這可全都是為了他好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果親愛的愛上除了我以外的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會很不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這樣講有點牽強耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特 明天早上我就會來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就暫時在這邊忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 竟然害我跌下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多美麗的夕陽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等太陽下山後 夜晚一到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的小彭芭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就去見妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢 我們就可以這樣…那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是給他逃出來了 這個親愛的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他還興致高昂得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道姊姊妳要…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我就是要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於熬到晚上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以和小彭芭一起看煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點…不太好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒事嘛 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:12:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們就等了\N期待的煙火大會快開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大哥呢? 他人在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八成又在哪兒追女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿我這個老哥沒有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不管他了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂拉 休可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看妳們做的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子就阻止也未免太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們兩個人看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.99,0:13:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的彭芭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在正背負著愛的十字架
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正要向妳飛奔而去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年才有一次這樣的慶典
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦?\N貧窮的百姓們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.81,0:13:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了共享這一天的歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感動 還是喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都辛勤地工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多新奇的煙火哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且今天晚上也有煙火大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是讓煙火技師們展身手的大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪會有各式各樣的煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂拉 妳看\N姊 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:14:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得有點罪惡感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 再不趕快就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要來不及了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小彭芭的約會就要來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險 我還以為會死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼搞的?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼搞的?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停不下來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳再怎麼等 他也不會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?\N是我們不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣 那就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特先生如果不來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就得不到幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小彭芭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就來了 妳要等我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?\N那是真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小彭芭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才好像聽到大哥的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彭芭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛\N振作點 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小彭芭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小彭芭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 凱洛特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彭芭小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特先生你成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來彭芭小姐是煙火技師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的那個大煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她為今天晚上的煙火大賽而做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為設計錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.54,0:18:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點火的開關變成在煙火上方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙火上方?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想耐打的凱洛特先生可能會有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才請你幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你居然連自己也一起打上去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓我太感動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的非常謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彭芭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞克斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了剛才的煙火我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重修舊好吧 可不可以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞克斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.51,0:18:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞克斯\N彭芭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞克斯跟彭芭…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彭芭小姐 這真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝妳幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再讓這個人跑掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特先生 非常謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 我只是遵守約定而已罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個史普露那大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會施法術的魔法師們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以法力支配人們 統治天下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為統治手段極為殘暴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無力抵抗的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能過著以淚洗面的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 對這些民眾而言 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.92,0:20:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們還有一線希望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是這裡有一群替天行道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專門懲治殘暴魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來去無蹤的正義戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們都稱他們為爆走獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 我是多塔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燦爛的生命雖短暫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有年輕的歲月似乎較長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.67,0:21:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是辛苦的歲月才是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫年輕和辛苦(日文)這兩個字這麼像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過年輕和辛苦相同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是字而已喲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有不少小孩子很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.81,0:21:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而大人也有他的辛苦之處
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 到底哪一個比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.69,0:21:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆走獵人 第五集
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湖畔的夢幻少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長大以後 也要愛我喔

